pullrequest.title: Bugfix for double_import_denier and better error message for h5_lock

content.raw: Using the better error message, we found the bug and fixed it. It was `labscript_utils.properties` importing h5py without importing h5\_lock. This bug was introduced in the recent serialised-attributes changes.
